	body(style="padding-bottom:10rem;")
		.container   
			block content
				include navbar
				br
				div
				.row
					.jumbotron
						.row
							.col-md-9
								h4(id='header') Guided List Creator
								p(id='comment') You can follow this wizard to quickly create an invite list	
